column8: Today, knowing who your customers are is one of the biggest problems facing offline businesses. Small and medium businesses with physical storefronts often struggle to identify their customers and manage their own technology stacks in order to piece together disconnected pieces of information. The process of customer identification should be transparent and simple for shoppers as one click, allowing businesses to combine all data silos into one tool that can bring together transaction information and customer data. Major point-of-sale (POS) providers are investing millions of dollars in improving their credit card processing part of the business, but there is little focus on customer identification and getting those customers to come back and shop more, increasing their average ticket value. We have taken on the difficult task of building the first platform that takes over the core customer identification experience. We connect all data from online and offline customer touchpoints into one single tool, allowing businesses to not only accurately identify their best customers, but also understand their purchase preferences and habits in order to embrace the entire customer experience and convert first-time shoppers into loyal fans, increase customer lifetime value, and drive more revenue for the business. It's simple: understand who your most valuable customers are, reward them, sell more. Repeat.

The simple answer is by turning to a global, online marketplace to solve their problem. However, not just any online marketplace. The best online marketplace for local glaziers to turn for targeting nationwide customers is Glass Genius, for several reasons. Let’s walk through what Glass Genius is, how it works, and how it can help glaziers expand their existing local customer base to a nationwide customer base. Glass Genius is the first global online marketplace that connects local glaziers, installers, and fabricators with consumers, contractors, and interior designers in need of their services. Never before has there been a platform created solely for the glass and mirror industry. If you sell glass or mirror products and you are ready to expand beyond your existing clients to a nationwide customer base, then Glass Genius is the place for you! How it works could not be easier. The user who forms the group (Group master) would set the buying price and invite other users to join his or her group. Invited members will see the set buying price and can choose to accept or reject the proposal made by the group master. If accepting the proposal, the user will be included inside the group. Once the market price matches the set buying price, the purchasing transaction will occur. Now the group will have to democratically vote to set the selling price. The logic for the set selling price will work the same as the set buying price.

At the same time, the platform makes it easier for students to get access to tens of thousands of online tutors in their subjects. Students can find tutors for everything from homework support to subject comprehension in areas where they are struggling. Students can also find support in completing assignments. The Bayise Tutor platform has been in development since 2019. It was recently incorporated in March 2021. We have already signed on dozens of tutors within a short period of time and now looking to expand our services to customers. Once fully operational, we expect hundreds of thousands to millions of students to signup and benefit from the Bayise Tutor platform. Apart from the tutoring services, we are also building an online social media platform, Bayise Social, that is aimed specifically at students and young people. column8: Lazy Horse Race Club is a metaverse horse racing world connected to a real life racing team through Club membership on the Cronos chain. Their Lazy Horse Ecosystem is composed of multiple parts that contribute to our overall vision and goals. In the Lazy Horse ecosystem, there are three main digital assets, HORSE - the Lazy Horse Founding Member NFT, PONY - the Lazy Horse Club Member NFT, and LHRC - the in-game token.These three assets are connected via the Lazy Horse Race Club - a play-to-earn gaming platform designed for Lazy Horse NFT owners. In game, the LHRC token is used to enter stakes races, speed up recovery and breeding times, and obtain upgrades.
